node.title: Human remains found in search for missing Victorian campers
node.alt: A composite image of a man outside and a woman holding a glass of wine at a restaurant
node.description: Police searching for the remains of missing Victorian campers Russell Hill and Carol Clay find human remains in bushland near Dargo, in the state's remote High Country.
node.content: ["Police searching for the remains of missing Victorian campers Russell Hill and Carol Clay\u00a0have found human remains in bushland near Dargo, in the state's remote High Country.", "They are yet to be formally\u00a0identified.", "More to come."]
